projects.name: Bitcoin Hyper
projects.desc: A Bitcoin Layer-2 protocol integrating Solana Virtual Machine (SVM) for smart contracts, DeFi, and NFTs, aiming to solve Bitcoin scalability with hybrid consensus and fast finality.

projects.narrative_thesis: Undervalued DeFi Infrastructure play with improving fundamentals; potential rerating as narrative gains mindshare.
